DROP EXTERNAL TABLE extDimTime;
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE extDimTime (
	[TimeSK] int,
	[TimeValue] datetime2(7),
	[TimeHour] int,
	[TimeMinute] int,
	[TimeSecond] int,
	[TimeMinuteOfDay] smallint,
	[TimeSecondOfDay] int
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Time',
	DATA_SOURCE = [silver_southridgedatalake02_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseDeltaFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.extDimTime
GO
